original_title: Fivestar Training with Wayne Rooney: Ball Control
overview: Train with Wayne Rooney and improve your soccer skills by completing workouts designed by the most accomplished soccer trainers in the world. Watch as Wayne and his team go through drills from shooting to dribbling, ball control, passing and more.
